<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Fiat Plan Argentina | Sitio Oficial 2026</title>
    <link href="https://googleapis.com" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cloudflare.com">
    <style>
        :root {
            --fiat-red: #B11016;
            --fiat-dark: #121212;
            --fiat-grey: #f0f0f0;
            --white: #ffffff;
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; }
        
        body { 
            background-color: var(--fiat-grey);
            background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns='http://w3.org' width='200' height='100' viewBox='0 0 200 100'%3E%3Ctext x='10' y='60' font-family='Arial' font-size='40' font-weight='bold' fill='%23000' fill-opacity='0.03'%3EFIAT%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E");
            color: #333;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        /* Navegación */
        nav {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 15px 8%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--fiat-red);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .logo-fiat { height: 45px; }

        .btn-header {
            background: var(--fiat-red);
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-header:hover { background: var(--fiat-dark); }

        /* Hero */
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.7), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), 
                        url('https://fiat.com.ar');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 60vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 4rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -2px; }
        .hero p { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 15px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; }

        /* Modelos Grid */
        .container { max-width: 1300px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 20px; }
        .title-section { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px; }
        .title-section h2 { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--fiat-dark); text-transform: uppercase; }
        .title-section hr { width: 60px; height: 5px; background: var(--fiat-red); border: none; margin: 15px auto; }

        .grid-modelos {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 35px;
        }

        .card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: 0.4s;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .card:hover { transform: translateY(-15px); box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(177, 16, 22, 0.15); }
        .card img { width: 100%; height: 220px; object-fit: contain; padding: 20px; background: #fff; }
        .card-content { padding: 25px; background: #fafafa; }
        .card-content h3 { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 900; text-transform: uppercase; }

        .btn-card {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--fiat-dark);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 700;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-card:hover { background: var(--fiat-red); }

        /* Formulario de Contacto */
        .contact-section {
            background: var(--fiat-dark);
            color: white;
            padding: 80px 5%;
            margin-top: 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .contact-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .contact-container h2 { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--fiat-red); }
        .contact-container p { margin-bottom: 40px; opacity: 0.8; }

        .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: left; }
        .form-group label { display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #ccc; }
        .form-group input, .form-group select, .form-group textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            background: #1a1a1a;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .form-group input:focus { border-color: var(--fiat-red); outline: none; }

        .btn-submit {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 18px;
            background: var(--fiat-red);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-submit:hover { background: #8e0e12; transform: scale(1.02); }

        /* WhatsApp Flotante */
        .ws-float {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 30px;
            right: 30px;
            background: #25d366;
            color: white;
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 35px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            z-index: 1000;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .ws-float:hover { transform: scale(1.1); }

        footer { background: #000; color: #555; text-align: center; padding: 40px; font-size: 0.8rem; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            .hero p { font-size: 1.1rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <img src="https://fiat.com.ar" alt="Fiat Oficial" class="logo-fiat">
        <a href="#contacto" class="btn-header">QUIERO MI FIAT</a>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero">
        <h1>GAMA FIAT 2026</h1>
        <p>ENTREGA PACTADA | CUOTAS EN PESOS</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="title-section">
            <h2>Elegí tu próximo 0km</h2>
            <hr>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-modelos">
            <!-- Cronos -->
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://fiat.com.ar" alt="Fiat Cronos">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Cronos</h3>
                    <a href="https://wa.me" class="btn-card">INFO WHATSAPP</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Strada -->
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://fiat.com.ar" alt="Fiat Strada">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Strada</h3>
                    <a href="https://wa.me" class="btn-card">INFO WHATSAPP</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Toro -->
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://fiat.com.ar" alt="Fiat Toro">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Toro</h3>
                    <a href="https://wa.me" class="btn-card">INFO WHATSAPP</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Pulse -->
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://fiat.com.ar" alt="Fiat Pulse">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Pulse</h3>
                    <a href="https://wa.me" class="btn-card">INFO WHATSAPP</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Fastback -->
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://fiat.com.ar" alt="Fiat Fastback">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3>Fastback</h3>
                    <a href="https://wa.me" class="btn-card">INFO WHATSAPP</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SECCIÓN FORMULARIO -->
    <section class="contact-section" id="contacto">
        <div class="contact-container">
            <h2>RECIBIR ASESORAMIENTO</h2>
            <p>Completá el formulario y un asesor oficial se contactará con vos en minutos.</p>
            
            <form action="#">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Nombre y Apellido</label>
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Ingresá tu nombre" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Número de WhatsApp</label>
                    <input type="tel" placeholder="11 7891-4211" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Modelo de Interés</label>
                    <select>
                        <option>Fiat Cronos</option>
                        <option>Fiat Strada</option>
                        <option>Fiat Toro</option>
                        <option>Fiat Pulse</option>
                        <option>Fiat Fastback</option>
                        <option>Fiat Fiorino</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label>Consulta adicional (Opcional)</label>
                    <textarea rows="3" placeholder="¿Tenés alguna duda?"></textarea>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">ENVIAR MI CONSULTA</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- WhatsApp Flotante -->
    <a href="https://wa.me" class="ws-float" target="_blank">
        <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i>
    </a>

    <footer>
        <p><strong>CONCESIONARIO OFICIAL FIAT ARGENTINA</strong></p>
        <p style="margin-top: 10px;">Ventas a todo el país. Los logos de FIAT son propiedad de Stellantis N.V. &copy; 2026</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
